      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-compression valvetrain that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential for precise torque vectoring. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension geometry is preserved with refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers, providing the neutral handling and tactile steering feedback this chassis is known for. While showing minor patina consistent with its age, the powertrain remains robust with excellent oil analysis results and no signs of rod bearing fatigue.",
